Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook Weekend: Tough as Old Boots
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cstzb7
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 18 Sep 2017
Magdeline Makola is a nurse, originally from South Africa, she was living in Scotland when she was kidnapped and locked in her car boot for ten days. Anthony Sosinski and John Aldridge are fishermen from Montauk, when John fell overboard in the middle of the night both men had to prove how tough they could be. Image: Silhouette of a person pushing a large stone uphill Credit: Nastco Show less